{"tid":1362704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[MTR 遍地開花] 東鐵綫車長的心聲","createTime":"2019-07-25T03:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:16:27.000Z","uid":55041,"like":1339,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":159,"replies":[{"pid":"26e7904cb80f65c52741a9349a8d76098736c933","tid":1362704,"uid":55041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:00:24.000Z","msg":"致港鐵行政總裁 金澤培先生<br />\n車務經理 鄭建寧先生<br />\n東鐵線列車員工經理 冼東昌先生<br />\n<br />\n敬啟者，我們乃一群關心7月21日元朗站受到恐怖襲擊的東鐵車長，對於公司於昨日(24日)所發出的聲明，我們感到遺憾及憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n7月21日晚上發生的元朗站恐怖襲擊事件中，不但乘客和車站同事遭襲擊，連車務控制中心（OCC）在元朗站面對巨大安全威脅時，仍貿然指令車長清客，妄顧列車乘客安全，最後造成大量受傷的情況，OCC理應負上責任。<br />\n<br />\nOCC掌管所有車站月台、大堂CCTV的監察權限。我們非常質疑在大堂恐怖襲擊事件發生時，究竟OCC有否第一時間用CCTV密切監察事態發展，如有，哪是否CCTV系統出現缺陷導致TC無法在情況惡化前及時作出應變措施？<br />\n<br />\n而事後在公司的新聞稿中，我們絲毫不見有提及過OCC決策失當，反指車長「沒有察覺暴力發生」，意圖將責任推卸在車長身上。導致該車長後來遭網民起底、受盡辱罵，我們認為公司的處理手法極度可恥及不負責任，令一眾前線員工對高層失去信心及背負罔顧乘客安全的罪名。<br />\n<br />\n對此我們要求公司完整交代7月21日元朗站受到恐怖襲擊經過，包括公開車站CCTV片段及相關完整無線電對話錄音，給員工和公眾合理解釋！<br />\n<br />\n港鐵每日有數以百萬計的乘客量，對於公司無法保障乘客及職員的安全，我們感到非常擔憂！眼見車站鐵閘能被暴徒輕易拉起，實在令人驚訝。我們促請公司檢討現行的措施及設備是否有能力應付同類情況，把損傷減至最低。<br />\n<br />\n不忿的東鐵綫車長們上<br />\n2019年7月25日<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xtZbNEW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxtZbNEW.jpg&h=63a419a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07RULrC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07RULrC.jpg&h=a00a679d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aavygyi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAavygyi.jpg&h=b4ea38f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5waiMF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5waiMF.jpg&h=6bc32aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqbp7E1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpqbp7E1.jpg&h=b5b58e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yRqa3dn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRqa3dn.jpg&h=11cea59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rjogej3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjogej3.jpg&h=719fe7c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vda2Uj4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVda2Uj4.jpg&h=103b4d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CRMtPTq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCRMtPTq.jpg&h=17d7749b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9kVeLrM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kVeLrM.jpg&h=a38a7406&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ffcca83d1c4d3348e5253b96c7ef1113c61ac60","tid":1362704,"uid":7355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21fa28c603ac906a1cd31ad622a2574b7201294f","tid":1362704,"uid":103693,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d074d4295f5b94847d573ee80902f8029193df5f","tid":1362704,"uid":270111,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8a89f4c44aa1fe30ee0f2871fac16a6f2b7c8039","tid":1362704,"uid":288777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:08:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89fa67891757453ecc34964eccf39bff46fc249b","tid":1362704,"uid":12988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4377d719d4f2a97ed0395463476cde9e2bcbd76f","tid":1362704,"uid":265707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:09:18.000Z","msg":"借個位 好文冇人幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[置頂] 打完飛機未，打完就入黎傾正經野呀！！ 727 反黑遊行 5+1 訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dpKaqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dpKaqS</a>"},{"pid